    "title": "Setting up a link to manage subscriptions"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Customers use the Settings > Apple Account > Subscriptions page in iOS to manage their subscriptions, including upgrading, downgrading, resubscribing, and canceling. When you offer subscriptions through the Advanced Commerce API, the Subscriptions page displays a “Manage in App” button.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "subscription-management-app-link.png",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You implement a subscription-management page in your app, and create a deep link URL to it that you submit to Apple. The Settings > Apple Account  > Subscriptions page then uses your deep link for the “Manage in App” button.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "To submit the subscription-management deep link URL for your eligible Advanced Commerce API app, use the Advanced Commerce API Access form on the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/in-app-purchase/advanced-commerce-api/",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " page.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Create the deep link by following these guidelines:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Follow universal link guidelines for the URL. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Xcode/allowing-apps-and-websites-to-link-to-your-content",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ensure the deep link lands on a page in your app that provides information about the subscription’s state and options for the customer to manage their subscription, for example, to change the plan, or resubscribe.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Optionally, provide a unique subscription-management deep link URL for each storefront.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
